script: You will be given three messages from different people Dr. Arron Kelvey, Seana Lynch, and Lisa-Marie Hastie.
Dr. Arron Kelvey: Bring to the meeting a fast land escape vehicle.
Seana Lynch: The time we will meet is when the sun leaves the sky.
Lisa-Marie Hastie: We will rendezvous where the land meets the sea.
Given the clandestine messages you have received, tell me as specifically as you can, when and where a meeting is going to happen and what you should bring.
